sticks to those social ills the government wants exposed 
criticism of senior leaders questioning oneparty rule or 
delving into sensitive subjects such as unrest in tibet are 
strictly off limits 
what the eightpage paper does offer particularly for a 
foreigner far from home is uptodate figures from world stock 
