hawaii university before coming to china 
frankel noted that although china was one of the biggest victims 
of japanese aggression in world war ii the china daily again 
following the government lead has made no appraisals of the role 
of the late emperor hirohito of japan in the war 
chen acknowledged that statements by the dalai lama the exiled 
tibetan religious leader appear only as background in articles 
where the chinese side condemns his calls for tibetan autonomy 
it would be better to report the straight news first he 
said 
