reporters are shocked at the way westerners find fault with their 
governments 
theres no bridging the gap that you reporters criticize 
your leaders 
but charles frankel said the paper shouldnt merely be judged by 
american standards 
it serves its purpose im glad this paper exists because it 
does present a window on the world 
