so far this year four people have been killed 
in the streets of washington every three days thats the rate of 
one every 18 hours 
the city has been dubbed the murder capital surpassing 
detroits percapita murder rate 
as of midday wednesday the police say 123 murders have 
occurred compared to 78 at this time last year 372 for all of 
last year the previous record for washington was 287 set in 1969 
in almost every case the victim is a black male and he meets 
his demise in one of the citys poorest neighborhoods according to 
